### [Joel Chapter 3](../../../bib/kjv/joe003.htm#001.md)

[Joel 3:9](../../../bib/kjv/joe003.htm#009.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_009">joe 3:9</span></span>

Prepare war

Verses 9-14 ([Joe 3:9-14](../../../bib/kjv/joe003.htm#009).md) refer to
Armageddon; verses 15, 16 ([Joe
3:15-16](../../../bib/kjv/joe003.htm#015).md) are parallel with ([Joe
2:30-32](../../../bib/kjv/joe002.htm#030).md). From verses 9 to 16 ([Joe
3:9-16](../../../bib/kjv/joe003.htm#009).md), we have a resume of ([Joe
2:9-32](../../../bib/kjv/joe002.htm#009).md).

